<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.7.3">
<l>teḷḷār kaṭalvāy viṭavāya ciṉavā ḷaravil tuyilamarntu</l>
<l>tuḷḷā varumāṉ viḻavāḷi turantā ṉirantāṉ māvalimaṇ</l>
<l>puḷḷār puṟavil pūṅkāvi pulaṅkoḷ mātar kaṇkāṭṭa</l>
<l>naḷḷār kamalam mukaṅkāṭṭum naṟaiyūr niṉṟa nampiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who begged for earth from Māvali, he who shot an arrow</l>
<l rend="indent">so a deer that came leaping fell</l>
<l>Having slept in the [milk-]white sea</l>
<l rend="indent">on a poison-mouthed, angry, cruel serpent,</l>
<l>Is the noble who stands in Naṟaiyūr where in bird-filled woodlands</l>
<l rend="indent">thick, full lotuses appear [like] faces,</l>
<l>As blooming blue lilies appear [like] eyes of ladies who rob the senses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
